analysis: The agent included an unsupported "emotion_depth" parameter in the "context" argument when calling poetry_theme_emotion_analyzer, causing a schema mismatch and preventing successful function invocation. Only "culture" was expected in the context.

The agent added an extra parameter ("safety_checks") to the locking_mechanism object in the function call, deviating from the expected function signature and causing no exact match for the adjust_seat_safety function.

The agent incorrectly included an extra "printTime" parameter and nested parameter values, resulting in a parameter structure that did not match the expected function signature, which only required the specified settings without additional or unnecessary fields.

The model omitted proper capitalization for the "genre" value ("pop" instead of "Pop"), resulting in a parameter mismatch with the expected function call signature. This prevented the evaluator from recognizing the function call as correct.

The agent incorrectly included an unsupported "intensity" parameter in the checkParameters object for the ContentAuthenticator_verifyOriginality function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch with the expected function signature.

The agent included an unsupported "eventTypes" parameter in the function call, which does not match the expected signature for CaseTimelineGenerator_generateTimeline and thus failed to make a valid function call.

The agent only processed one audio file ("recording_light.mp3" with light intensity) instead of handling all three recordings with their specified correction intensities, failing to fulfill the complete multi-step request.
The agent incorrectly formatted the year "100 AD" as "100" instead of the required four-digit format "0100", resulting in a parameter mismatch and no valid function call match for that instance.

The agent made only one function call without specifying any patient ID or date range, instead of making individual hospital_record_fetch calls with the required parameters for each patient as expected. It failed to decompose the multi-patient request properly.
